reviews.text: Nice and peaceful atmosphere, clean, well maintained station, staff on site for help. Offers good service

Trains always terminate, blonde old looking woman working today was rude and lazy. Asked a question about if there’s any met trains going to rainers lane as there was nothing on the board. She said ‘yeah loads’ i replied saying where as there was nothing on the board. She just said ‘well it’s there’ and huffed and looked away as if I was causing her a massive problem. After checking again eventually a train popped up with a 17 minute wait which doesn’t seem like there’s loads to me? I understand sometimes there’s problems with train lines etc but when I come to ask a genuine question you could be a bit more helpful and don’t act so rude.
